title: RitFit Leg Press Hack Squat Machine, Professional Adjustable Leg Press Machine for Home Gym with Linear Bearing, Specialty Hack Squat Machine for Full Lower Body Workout with Weight Storage Posts
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Weight Machines › Leg Machines
description: Experience the stability and versatility of our leg press and hack squat machine. Angled at 45 degree, the entire structure ensures a safe and comfortable workout. Target various leg muscles utilizing the dual function of the inclined leg press and hack squat. The wider and thicker cushions are wrapped in high quality leather that is durable and easy to clean, allowing you to enjoy a more comfortable experience. Our machine prioritizes safety with solid guide rods, cushioning pads, and two storage for barbell plates. Adjustable footplate accomodate your body shape, providing an ergonomic exercise experience. Packed separately, we ensure minimal wear and tear during shipping. Expect packages to arrive on different dates, but rest assured as we will keep a close eye on the logistics for you.
features: 【Stability & Versatile Workout】This two-in-one leg press and hack squat machine is adapted linear bearings rather than rolling ones, and it is constructed of heavy-duty high tensile beefy steel. Beyond that, there are two weight plate storage holders at the rear bottom, when stacked up, greatly enhance machine's stability when in motion. By adjusting the placement of your feet on the foot plate, you can focus more on training isolating muscle groups.

【Comfort & Smooth Exercise Experience】This leg press and hack squat gym machine features thick shoulder and backrest cushion wrapped in premium anti-slip and wear-resistant leather surface, providing ultimate and long-lasting comfort to ease your strain and stress, and protecting your bones and joints during your bodybuilding. Solid metal guide rods (sled) and aluminium alloy grips on both sides upgrade your workout experience without jerk motions.

【Safety & Considerate Design】The weight carriage fits 2'' plates, and Max 1200 lbs plate loading satisfies most users' needs. It is beginner-friendly, for experienced pro, you can do one leg at a time. Large diamond-plated footplate increases friction, preventing accidental sideslipping while in use. Two cushionings at the sled's bottom soften sudden impact with less noise. The triangular piece at the base of the back support also enhances overall stability.

【Multiple Adjustments】As a well-crafted design, there are 5 angle choices for hack squat and 3 for leg press setting, accomodating different sized athelets. The side rail (safety catches attached) handles can be pushed out to unlock the sled. After you are done with your set, pull both handles inward yourself to lock the sled in your designated lockout position. With a quick flip of the back pad and lowering of the leg press footplate, you can switch workouts in seconds to perform hack squat.

【Separate Package】Our leg press and hack squat machine will be shipped in two separate packages to minimize the possibility of wear and tear due to collisions. Your packages may arrive on different dates. If you only receive part of the shipment, please be patient as we continuously monitor your logistics status. Backed by RitFit Lifetime Limited Warranty and friendly customer service, buy with confidence in RitFit!

title: Valor Fitness Calf Raise Machine - Adjustable Seated Leg Exercise - Plate Loaded Strength Training Workout Calves Home Gym Equipment CC-5
inStockText: Only 4 left in stock - order soon.
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Weight Machines › Leg Machines
features: HEAVY DUTY CALF RAISE MACHINE- The CC-5 Calf Machine is constructed with 12-gauge steel for strength and durability. The diamond plated foot plates give you stability when performing calf raises, while chrome plated sleeves hold weights.

BUILD CALF STRENGTH- Use this leg machine to target the soleus calf muscle and accelerate calf muscle growth in your workout! Calf raises also help to treat and prevent shin splints by strengthening the calf, as well as assisting in Achilles rehab.

ADJUSTABLE CALF MACHINE- Using steel popper pins, the knee pad can be adjusted to 6 different vertical positions, and 5 horizontal positions. After finding optimal position, lift the knees up and move the safety bar for a full range of motion!

HOW TO PERFORM CALF RAISES- Flex your calves and explode through the balls of your feet at full ankle extension and raise the heels. Hold this position briefly and return to the starting position by dropping the heels below the foot plate!

ADDITIONAL- Improve strength, power, and performance! Max weight load of 350 lb. Total footprint measures 51.25" x 25" x 36". Meant for home gym workout and light-commercial use, or in physical therapy/injury prevention facilities!

aPlusContent.title: Product Description
aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
Seated Calf Raise Machine – Ultimate Lower Leg Workout Equipment 
The video showcases the product in use.The video guides you through product setup.The video compares multiple products.The video shows the product being unpacked.
Seated Calf Raise Machine – Plate-Loaded Lower Leg Workout Equipment for Strength Training. Designed for use with 2" Olympic Bumper Plates, this durable machine targets calf muscles for effective lower body workouts. Perfect for home gyms or commercial use to build strength and endurance. 
Seated Calf Raise Machine – Lower Body Workout Equipment for Calf Development 
Take your leg day workouts to the next level with the Seated Calf Raise Machine, designed for fitness enthusiasts and professionals aiming for complete lower body strength and muscle definition. Perfect for home gyms, light-commercial settings, and rehabilitation centers, this machine focuses on building and strengthening your soleus calf muscles, providing them with the targeted attention often overlooked in conventional workouts. 
Built with 12-gauge steel, the Seated Calf Raise Machine is engineered for durability and long-term use. The chrome-plated weight-bearing sleeves are designed to accommodate 2-inch Olympic-style plates, while the diamond-plated footplate provides exceptional stability during every lift. This robust construction ensures a secure and effective calf workout, even under heavy loads. 
Specifically crafted to strengthen and grow the soleus muscle, the seated calf raise exercise plays a pivotal role in enhancing overall leg strength and performance. Regular use can also help prevent shin splints, strengthen the Achilles tendon, and improve ankle stability, making it an excellent tool for athletes and individuals recovering from lower leg injuries. 
This user-friendly machine features steel popper pins for quick and hassle-free adjustments. The knee pad can be positioned in six vertical and five horizontal positions, accommodating users of various heights and leg lengths. Adjustments are simple: elevate your knees, move the safety bar aside, and enjoy a full range of motion to maximize your results. 
By pushing through the balls of your feet, the machine ensures optimal calf muscle activation. The combination of a controlled release and a short hold at peak contraction intensifies muscle engagement, leading to faster strength and growth. This machine is ideal for strength training, rehabilitation, or achieving aesthetic goals. 
Weight Capacity: Handles a maximum load of 350 lbs., catering to beginners and experienced athletes alike.
Compact Design: With dimensions of 51.25" x 25" x 36", this machine is space-efficient, making it perfect for home gyms and light-commercial setups.
Optional Floor Mounting: For added safety and stability during heavy lifts, the machine can be floor-mounted.
Strengthened calf muscles are essential for activities like running, jumping, and climbing. A strong soleus helps absorb impact, reducing the risk of injuries such as shin splints or Achilles tendon strains. Regular use of this machine also promotes better performance in sports and functional movements. 
This machine offers the flexibility to incorporate calf raises into a variety of training regimens, from general fitness to specialized rehabilitation programs. Its compact design and adaptability make it suitable for athletes, physical therapy professionals, and personal trainers.

Built with 12-gauge steel, the Seated Calf Raise Machine is engineered for durability and long-term use. The chrome-plated weight-bearing sleeves are designed to accommodate 2-inch Olympic-style plates, while the diamond-plated footplate provides exceptional stability during every lift. This robust construction ensures a secure and effective calf workout, even under heavy loads. 
Specifically crafted to strengthen and grow the soleus muscle, the seated calf raise exercise plays a pivotal role in enhancing overall leg strength and performance. Regular use can also help prevent shin splints, strengthen the Achilles tendon, and improve ankle stability, making it an excellent tool for athletes and individuals recovering from lower leg injuries. 
This user-friendly machine features steel popper pins for quick and hassle-free adjustments. The knee pad can be positioned in six vertical and five horizontal positions, accommodating users of various heights and leg lengths. Adjustments are simple: elevate your knees, move the safety bar aside, and enjoy a full range of motion to maximize your results. 
By pushing through the balls of your feet, the machine ensures optimal calf muscle activation. The combination of a controlled release and a short hold at peak contraction intensifies muscle engagement, leading to faster strength and growth. This machine is ideal for strength training, rehabilitation, or achieving aesthetic goals. 
Weight Capacity: Handles a maximum load of 350 lbs., catering to beginners and experienced athletes alike.
Compact Design: With dimensions of 51.25" x 25" x 36", this machine is space-efficient, making it perfect for home gyms and light-commercial setups.
Optional Floor Mounting: For added safety and stability during heavy lifts, the machine can be floor-mounted.
Strengthened calf muscles are essential for activities like running, jumping, and climbing. A strong soleus helps absorb impact, reducing the risk of injuries such as shin splints or Achilles tendon strains. Regular use of this machine also promotes better performance in sports and functional movements. 
This machine offers the flexibility to incorporate calf raises into a variety of training regimens, from general fitness to specialized rehabilitation programs. Its compact design and adaptability make it suitable for athletes, physical therapy professionals, and personal trainers.

title: Mikolo Power Cage, 2000LB Squat Rack, Dual Pulley Cable Crossover System, Multi-function Free Weight Home Gym Workout Machine with Attachments
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Racks & Cages › Power Cages
description: Mikolo Power Cage, 2000LB Squat Rack, Dual Pulley Cable Crossover System, Multi-function Free Weight Home Gym Workout Machine with Attachments
features: [Independent Dual Pulley System] Unlike the common power cage, the HR05 has an independent 1:1 ratio double pulley system on both sides of the frame. 1:1 means that the weight you train is the weight you load. And the weight capacity of power rack will double. The independent pulley system allows you to complete super set, drop set, co-training and other gym workouts without being limited by the home gym weight stack cap.

[4-IN-1 Home Gym Partner] HR05 combines a power rack, multi-grip pull up bar, cable crossover machine and 360° landmine into one machine. At the same time, the pulley system has been upgraded to give you a seamless and stable movement experience. The improved sliding sleeve ensures smooth operation while protecting the pulley from damage. Gross Weight: 205 lbs. The machine boasts a maximum capacity of up to 2000 lbs.

[Unique Column] More holes have been drilled into the HR05 power cage's posts at 1-inch spacing, giving you a total of 30 height options. There are also digital markers on the side to help you locate quickly. In addition, we use the standard 2"x 2" column, which can be adapted to a variety of accessories on the market to unlock more training possibilities. The tube thickness of 2 mm effectively ensures the stability of the power rack.

[Space-saving Design] Another major feature of the HR05 is the space savings, the frame design is closer to half rack, compared to most power racks, its space can be reduced by nearly two-thirds. In addition, we are equipped with more weight storage areas in the middle of HR05, which can not only effectively organize the space of the home gym, but also increase the stability of the shelves.

[Fully equipped & versatile] The HR05 power cage comes with all the attachments you may need more of in your daily training. including 4 free handle attachments, 2 safety spotter pins, dip bars, j hooks, and T-bar row attachment. This provides a wide range of exercises, such as wide & narrow lat pull-downs, T-bar rows, seated cable rows, bench presses, squats, deadlifts, bicep curls, triceps extensions, pull-ups, chin-ups, dips, and more.

description: This wide and high calf raise bar is very sturdy with great paint work. If you are looking for a useful calf raise platform, this is a great addition to your home gym. Easy to use and convenient to be taken to anywhere you want to do the calf raise exercises. With this calf raise block, you can exercise your calf muscles well and effectively. If you have any questions or problems about our calf raise bar, please feel free to contact us.
features: Well Built: Our calf raise bar is heavy in weight and heavy duty in construction. It is not easy to break. Also don’t worry about the slippery problem.There is Anti slip texture protrusion on the surface of the calf block. Weight bearing is about 880lbs.

Rubber Feet: This calf raise bar is equipped with four rubber feet which make it more stable. The rubber feet give good traction on the rubberized floor of your home gym. Without strong rubber smell and can protect your floor.
Strengthen Calf Muscles: You can exercise your calf muscles well and effectively with our extra high and wide steel standing calf raise machine. Besides this, you can do toe lifts to work the shins.
Easy to use: You can use the calf raise machine with a Smith Machine or a squatting frame, just put your foot or feet on it.

Professional customer service: For our high calf raise bar, we will provide quality assurance. If you have any problems about this calf block, please feel free to contact us, we will give you a quickly and satisfactory answer.

aPlusContent.title: Product Description
aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
Why you should get this GMWD seated raise machine? 
Distinguished from the ordinary standing calf raise, this machine can help you better find the power point, more correctly focus on the calf muscle is training. 
It also reduces the burden on your knees. 
Why you should choose GMWD calf machine over other calf machines? 
“Value for money" is the answer. This home calf machine is optimized from commercial fitness equipment. This calf workout machine is constructed with 12-gauge steel for strength and durability. Gross weight: 56LBS. 
What does this machine work for? 
Focus on your calf muscles (gastrocnemius and soleus). Say goodbye to weak calves and hello to toned, strong muscles with GMWD calf raise machine. 
Is the sitting calf training machine suitable for beginners? 
Absolutely, an excellent choice for beginners to build their calf muscles.

It is a good choice for home workouts.
features: 【Professional and Effective Exercise Device】This seated calf raise machine is designed to exercise the calves and enhance the strength, power and lines of the calves. It ensures correct posture and maximizes muscle activation during exercise, resulting in stronger, more powerful calves.

【Sturdy】The seated calf raise machine is constructed from sturdy commercial tubing. The special bearing structure is stronger, ensuring safety and stability during movement and avoiding the violent shaking problem common with other products. Maximum load-bearing capacity is 660LBS.

【Adjustable Settings】The height of the calf machine leg pad can be adjusted in 4 levels, and the distance of the support rod front and back can be adjusted in 4 levels to adapt to people of different heights to adjust the comfortable training posture. Height Recommendation: Up to 6'0". Detachable barbell sleeves for use with 1&2 inch barbell plates!(SALES DO NOT INCLUDE WEIGHT PLATES)

【Multifunctional Calf Exerciser】There are currently 2 types of exercise methods available, with barbell plates and elastic bands to choose from. There are 4 elastic band hooks attached to the elastic bands on both sides, which can be connected to the elastic bands to increase resistance and have better leg muscle building effect.

【Excellent Comfort Design】The flat leg compression pad can relieve pressure on the legs, and the wider and thicker seat is more comfortable. Equipped with extended anti-slip pedals to keep it stable and not wobbly during exercise.

aPlusContent.title: Product Description
aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
What is a Slant Board? 
A slant board is a flat-surfaced device made from durable wood or lightweight plastic material and is used to keep our muscles and tendons in perfect shape. By standing in a slant position on this board, you improve the performance of your muscles for exercise and cut down on cases of injury. If you're an athlete or someone suffering from Achilles tendon injuries, this board will help to relieve the pain. 
What are the Benefits of a Slant Board? 
Any health-conscious person will be quick to learn the advantages of this simple yet powerful device. Do you know why? A slant board is useful not leg-related pains and injuries, but also for proper blood circulation and the relief of back pain. Here are the benefits of using a slant board. 
The calf plays a great role in our daily activities and movement such as running, walking, jumping, and standing. Hence, you need a slant board to help you stretch them and make them flexible.
It helps to prevent inflammation which often comes with pain.
Using a slant board allows you to protect the Achilles tendon which is the strongest tendon in the body.
It's also useful for relieving the stress around muscles which tend to ache after exercise.
Preventive medicine also values slant boards to ensure that possible leg injuries are avoided.
A slant board helps in the circulation of blood to the leg to prevent swellings.
PREMIUM MATERIAL 
Made of high-quality Lauan hardwood plywood, stronger and last longer than others made of birch and pine plywood. 
EXTRA SIDE-HANDLE 
The original design of the side handles makes the board easy to carry. 
ANTI-SLIP DESIGN 
Anti-Slip design on both surface and bottom offers the best safety protection.

What is Squat Wedge?
Heel Elevated Squats and Calf Raises in Daily Weighted Squats and Leg Strength Workouts for Depth and Training Efficiency

Promotes a balance between strength and flexibility to avoid muscle and knee injuries due to weak heel support during weightlifting squats 
better squats

Improve strength training efficiency

Improve your squat performance 
Squat Wedge helps you maintain proper posture and prevents muscle damage caused by poor posture by raising your heels and releasing pressure on your lower back, knees and hips. Improve your balance and coordination, and increase your training efficiency. 
perfect replacement for the heavy duty wooden Slant Board

UNMERA Squat Wedge Block can perform deadlifts, Romanian deadlifts, calf stretches, lunges, Jefferson curls and more!

aPlusContent.title: Product Description
aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
Stretching and toning the tibialis anterior is important for people who need to improve their athletic ability and reduce post-workout pain, especially those who participate in running, kickball or jumping sports. 
Building strong and relaxed tibialis anterior helps minimize the negative effects of the high impact of the feet hitting the ground so often. I'm sure this will be your dream training equipment —— Tibialis Trainer 
What does exercise your shin muscles give you? 
A. Strengthens the lower limbs and improves explosive power 
B. Strengthens the muscle groups on the front side of the calf 
C. Stabilizes the ankle and improve your balance 
D. Preventing sports injuries to the calves, ankles and feet 
E. Prevention of knee pain and shin splints 
F. Reduced risk of stress fractures 
4 Thick Foam Pads 
Exercise is more comfortable with the addition of 2 thick foam pads to the original, and you can work out even with your shoes off. 
High Quality Barbell Clamp 
Secure barbell plates efficiently and say goodbye to wobbling. Tip: Press and hold the black button hard to unlock it easily. 
Quick Release Pin 
Unique limit design. Double securing to avoid barbell clamps falling off due to excessive weight on the weight plates.

aPlusContent.title: Product Description
aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
ProStretch Calf Stretcher for Plantar Fasciitis & Achilles Tendonitis 
The video showcases the product in use.The video guides you through product setup.The video compares multiple products.The video shows the product being unpacked.
Do I need to use the ProStretch while wearing shoes? Can I just wear socks? 
The ProStretch should be used while wearing shoes with a supportive, rubber sole. 
What if my foot hangs off of the ProStretch? 
ProStretch Original is intended for shoe sizes 12 or below. If your foot hangs off, that is absolutely fine. You are still able to obtain full use of the device even if it may look a little funny. 
Why is the ProStretch better than just normal stretching (on a wall, steps, or a curb)? 
The ProStretch holds your foot in an optimal angle to get a superior stretch. 
What is the difference between the ProStretch & the ProStretch Plus? 
The ProStretch Original weight limit is 250 pounds & fits shoe sizes up to 12. The ProStretch Plus is a little longer and wider which accommodates up to shoe size 14 and a weight limit of 300 pounds. It's adjustable with a removeable toe lift. 
Do I have to stand while using the ProStretch or can it be used in a seated position? 
The ProStretch can be used to provide therapy for a number of indications. Exercises and positions for each indication are provided in our instruction manual that comes with the product and video.

aPlusContent.title: Product Description
aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
Squat wedge block 
PERFORM DEEPER SQUATS 
The 15 degree incline is perfect for people looking to deepen their squat and increase their range of motion. Just starting out? This angle is great for beginners, too! 
KEEP YOUR HEELS PLANTED 
Having trouble keeping your heels down while you squat? Choosing an intermediate, 30 degree angle might help. The increased angle also begins engaging your quads more. 
TARGET YOUR QUADS 
Looking to work on your quadriceps? A 40 degree incline turns your squat into a quad-dominant exercise, specifically activating and strengthening these muscles for a targeted workout.

title: Body-Solid (SCB26) Calf Raise Block and Squat Platform - Solid Steel Incline Wedge for Enhanced Lower Body Workouts, 2000 lb Capacity
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Weight Machines › Leg Machines
description: Product DescriptionThe Body-Solid Calf Squat Block (SCB26) is designed to help keep the focus in the calf muscles when performing calf muscle exercise such as calf raises or squats. The combination squat platform and calf block has a weight capacity of 2000 pounds and a non-slip surface. The 2-bolt assembled squat block features a solid steel frame and a welded carrying handle. At 26 inches long the squat rack allows you to elevate heels for a better balance so you can better target the calf muscles. The Body-Solid Calf Squat Block (SCB26) measures 26 x 18 x 6.5 inches (L x W x H). It is commercial rated backed by the Body-Solid In-Home Warranty and Commercial warranty.Amazon.comThe Body Solid SCB26 is half squat platform and half calf block, letting you perform both stable squat exercises and intense calf raise exercises with a full range of motion and complete comfort. The unit offers a full 26-inch-long squat platform that invites the user to elevate his or her heels for better balance and concentration, along with an 18-inch-long by 6.5-inch-tall calf block that stretches and contracts your calf muscles. Plus, the SCB26 is durable and long lasting, with a solid-steel, two-bolt assembly that includes a welded carrying handle and a textured, no-slip surface. Offering a 2,000-pound capacity, the SCB26 carries a lifetime warranty.
features: INDUSTRY LEADER: For 30+ years, Body Solid has held the widest array of products designed to meet the demands of the ever-changing fitness industry (home gym, free weight machines, treadmills, bikes, ellipticals, weight plates, kettlebells, dumbbells, flooring, accessories and more). Our products are cutting edge and reliable and are built for Life……Your Life.

HEAVY-DUTY CONSTRUCTION FOR PEAK PERFORMANCE: Engineered with solid steel and a 2000 lb. capacity, this squat and calf raise platform is built to withstand the rigors of intense daily workouts. The diamond-textured, no-slip surface ensures a secure footing, allowing you to focus on form and maximize gains without the risk of equipment failure.

ENHANCED STABILITY AND RANGE OF MOTION: The 18” long Calf Raise platform with a 6-1/2” height promotes a full range of motion for calf exercises, while the 26” long Squat platform allows for optimal heel elevation, ensuring a stable and concentrated workout experience.

UNLOCK LOWER BODY POWER: Take your lower body strength and flexibility to new heights with this versatile squat and calf raise platform. Designed for serious athletes and fitness enthusiasts, its durable construction and thoughtful design prioritize safety, effectiveness, and longevity in your training regimen.

EASY TO ASSEMBLE AND TRANSPORT: With a simple 2 bolt assembly and a welded carrying handle, this squat and calf raise platform is user-friendly, easy to set up, and can be moved with ease, making it an excellent addition to any home gym or professional fitness center.

title: GMWD Chest Press Machine, 1250LBS Bench Press Machine with Independent Converging Arms, 7+5 Adjustable Incline Chest Press Machine for Home Gym, 30° Target Upper Chest, Black
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Weight Machines › Upper Body Machines
features: 【Target Your Upper Chest】Our V2 incline bench press machine is specifically designed with a 30° incline angle, widely recognized as the best angle for upper chest workouts. People normally ignore it, but to have a full-grown chest, it is important. It's time to break with the traditional bench press machine.

【High-duty Constructed Bench】GMWD V2 incline chest press machine constructed with 50 x 50(mm), 11 gauge steel tube. Featuring a unique triangle structure and heavy-duty steel design, this machine provides sturdy stability, and are solid enough to load 1250lbs, 200lbs capacity of each weight holder plus 450lbs capacity of the weight bench. Note:The Detachable Sleeve can fit both 1'' & 2'' plates. Feel free to put weights on it!

【7+5 Fully Adjustable】5 Exercise Starting Position: The machine is equipped with an adjustable seat(5 positions), which allows you to easily adapt the device to the height of the exerciser. Thanks to the adjustable backrest angle, the machine offers 7 exercise starting positions. Such variety allows you to increase the effectiveness of each workout and build chest sculpture faster.

【Special Gas-Spring Design】Are you still struggling with adjusting the height of the work arms? Our machine will solve your problem perfectly with a unique gas-spring design. Simply A PRESS (press on the arms) and A PULL (pull out the pin), and the work arms will automatically rise. Release the pin when arms reach the desired position. No longer face the inconvenience of manually adjusting the height with your two hands. Note: Avoid putting too much weight on it; the best use is with an empty arm.

【Independent Converging Work Arms】The biggest surprise is that the arms are independent and cylinder design on each arm for easy adjustment. Can provide unilateral training to ensure muscle symmetry. Fit for beginners and regular gym-goers alike!

【Ready for International Chest Day?】After a relaxed weekend, many seek that invigorating chest pump to beat the Monday blues, and what better way to get someone motivated to workout on Monday than starting the week with chest training? Ready to ace your next chest day? Join GMWD, and let’s make every Monday count!

【Brand Support】GMWD is a professional fitness brand committed to designing and manufacturing the best home gym equipment. This adjustable incline chest machine overall dimension: 46.9"(L)*46.9"(W)*41.3"(H). If there is any question about this weight bench machine, please feel free to contact us, we are always here for you.

Why do we say that our machine is also suitable for beginners? 
V2 incline press machine can be suitable for beginners as it provides a guided movement and allows for easy adjustments to the weight and angle. 
Can the incline chest press machine help strengthen other muscles besides the chest? 
Certainly, the incline press machine primarily works the chest muscles (pectoralis major and minor), as well as the triceps and shoulders. It can also engage the core muscles as you stabilize your body during the exercise. 
Why should I consider using this incline bench press machine? 
Specifically designed with a 30° incline angle, widely recognized as the best angle for upper chest workouts, and with other 6 backrest positions to choose, our machine helps to build your chest sculpture faster. 
Why choose this machine with vertical grip options? 
Verticval grips can offer better ergonomic support, reducing strain on wrist, elbow and shoulder. With vertical grips, you can also allow for targeting upper chest more precisely, enhancing the overall effectiveness of your fitness routine.

title: Body-Solid Leverage Squat/Calf Machine
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Weight Machines › Leg Machines
description: The Body-Solid Leverage Squat and Calf Raise Machine (GSCL360) handles the heaviest loads with ease to help you develop explosive lower-body power. The squat is the ultimate exercise for building mass and strength in your thighs, glutes, calves, and lower back. This squat machine is designed to handle massive weight loads of over 800 pounds (Olympic weight plates sold separately), and it is specifically engineered to help to eliminate the risks of this essential exercise while enhancing its benefits and increasing its effectiveness. The heavy-gauge diamond plate foot platform is set to a perfect 20-degree pitch, delivering optimal development of the quadriceps and glutes. The innovative calf raise block is round instead of square, eliminating the painful edge and providing a deep pre-stretch for maximum calf-blasting workouts. This squat machine is designed to handle massive weight loads of over 800 pounds (Olympic weight plates sold separately), and it is specifically engineered to help to eliminate the risks of this essential exercise while enhancing its benefits and increasing its effectiveness. The heavy-gauge diamond plate foot platform is set to a perfect 20-degree pitch, delivering optimal development of the quadriceps and glutes. The innovative calf raise block is round instead of square, eliminating the painful edge and providing a deep pre-stretch for maximum calf-blasting workouts. Exclusive DuraFirm shoulder pads are engineered to conform to the shoulders and back for a safe and secure fit during the heaviest lifts. This squat machine is constructed with an extra-large 3- by 3-inch high-tensile-strength mainframe made with 12-gauge steel welded on all four sides, allowing it to stand up to massive workloads in high-traffic gyms and clubs. When assembled, the Body-Solid Leverage Squat and Calf Raise Machine measures 62 by 43 by 56 inches (L x W x H) and weighs 170 pounds. It is backed by the Body-Solid Lifetime In-Home and Full Commercial .

breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Weight Machines › Leg Machines
features: PREMIUM QUALITY MATERIAL: The tibialis trainer is carefully crafted with high strength iron tubing and HDR foam to ensure long lasting and comfortable use. And the surface has super hard anti-scratch spraying, which makes the product won't have scratches easily and ensures the integrity of the product. It is also equipped with high quality clamps to hold the barbell plates tightly.

SIZE AND LOAD: 14.6 inches long, 11 inches wide and 8.7 inches high, fits adult and youth feet of all sizes. The loadable sleeve measures 9.4 inches in length, fits 2-inch Olympic-size metal weightlifting plates and rubber competition cushion plates, and weighs approximately 4.7 pounds overall, with a maximum weight capacity of 200 pounds.

STRONG AND DURABLE: Our tib bar is a complete product that is not removable, there is no hassle of product parts coming loose, allowing the product to last longer. Made of steel, the tibialis trainer makes the product more durable and easy to install.

EXERCISE MUSCLE: Professional tibialis anterior muscle exercise equipment that trains and strengthens the tibialis anterior muscle. By targeting and strengthening the tibialis anterior muscle, it improves balance and flexibility and reduces the risk of lower leg, ankle and foot injuries.

WIDELY USED: Ideal for a variety of workouts to train and strengthen the tibialis anterior muscles for a variety of sports such as explosive running, soccer sprints, bouncing, diving or snowboarding. This builds strength in the shins, knees, tibia and ankles and improves overall leg strength.

aPlusContent.title: Product Description
aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
TIB BAR 
Benefits of stretching and exercising the tibialis anterior muscles： 
Use the tib bar to professionally target our shin muscles, which are very important to our movement, especially important for those who participate in running or jumping activities. Strong and relaxed tibialis anterior muscles can help to counteract the negative effects of the high impact of the feet constantly hitting the ground. 
What muscles will be worked with a tib bar? 
Achilles tendon strengthening exercise
Ankle strengthening exercise
Calf muscle group exercise
Front thigh muscles group exercise
Loading rod 
Made of high-strength tubing to hold 2-inch diameter barbell plates. 
Sturdy clips 
High-quality sturdy clips, tight and reliable. Effectively secures the barbell plates and prevents them from swaying back and forth. 
HDR Foam 
HDR foam over shin trainers to add comfort to your workout. 
How to use the tib bar? 
Place the 2-inch Olympic plates on the barbell, make sure they are pushed onto the barbell clamps and secure them tightly with the locking clips. Once secured, you can begin practicing with the tib bar.

inStockText: Only 18 left in stock - order soon.
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Racks & Cages › Power Cages
features: 【1:1 Ratio for heavier resistance 】: Enjoy a full-body workout with ease using our premium power cage, featuring an integrated Lat Pulldown System and Low Row System. like the lat pull-down, Tricep pushdowns, biceps curls, and face pull. The Lat/low row system is more budget-friendly and compact for the home gym than the cage with FT.Its multi-grip pull-up bar allows for varied grip positions, targeting different muscle groups for maximum results.

【Seamless Adjustability 】: Experience seamless transitions between exercises with 17 adjustable height positions, clearly marked for convenience. Whether you're performing squats, bench presses, or rows, easily customize the setup to suit your preferences and body type. 87" height pull-up bar allows you to perform better pull-ups. You can do unlimited exercises in this full power cage.

【Space-efficient Design】: Maximize your home gym space without compromising on functionality. Our power rack boasts a compact footprint(22SQFT) while offering ample storage options, including weight storage pins and handle storage hooks, keeping your workout area tidy and organized.

【Premium Features】: Built to last, C3 power cage comes fully equipped with essential attachments, including Safety spotters, dip bars, J-hooks, and a T-bar row attachment. Plus, enjoy added convenience with included accessories like carabiner clips, extension chains for cables, and weight holder clips, elevating your workout experience to new heights.

【Unmatched Stability】This strength training power cage features 14 gauge, 2*2'' steel tube. The new steel structure combine with triangle connectors is more durable, and it could rate 1200 lbs. Stronger bearing capacity allows you to challenge larger weights. Dimensions: 43.3"(L)*39.4"(W)*87"(H) | Assembled Weight: 167lbs. (Please confirm the height is higher than 87 inches before buying)

breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Weight Machines › Leg Machines
description: Shnlie Tib Bar, Tibialis Trainer, Tibia Dorsi Calf Raise Machine Accessories: 4 Foam Pads: Thickened foam adds friction and softness for better control, allowing one to focus on exercise and stay comfortable, can be used even with shoes off. Clamps Collar: Effectively fix the weight plate to prevent back and forth shaking. Limit Pin: Innovative designs, double protection and fixation to prevent the buckle from slipping. 2 inch diameter / 1 inch diameter: 2 sizes to choose from. Suitable for 2 inchd Olympic Plates or 1 inch dumbbell pieces (depending on the size you purchase). Function: Strengthen your leg muscle and level up your regular leg exercise.  Strengthen the tibialis anterior, improves lower body movement. Helps to avoid the potential problem to the knee, shin, and ankles.
features: 【Perfect Addition】 Don't forget about your tibialis muscles during leg day, Shnlie Tibialis Bar makes it easy to focus on this often neglected area. It also easily trains your thighs and calves, and is the perfect addition to your strength training!

【Injury Reduction】 Using the tib bar also helps strengthen the muscles, tendons and ligaments around the ankle joint, reducing the risk of injury to the calf, ankle and foot, increading leg stability and balance.
【4 foam pads]】Different from other tibialis trainers, we add 2 foam pads on the original basis, which will not hurt your feet even if you take off your shoes. It is more comfortable.

【Effective Accessories】It comes with high quality collar that hold the weight plate tightly to the base to prevent movement when in use. It also comes with newly designed limit pins for double protection.

【Product Guarantee】 The tib bar has a sturdy steel construction that is so durable that it will not bend or crack from heavy or prolonged use. We offer lifetime after-sales service, so you can contact us anytime with questions.

aPlusContent.title: Product Description
aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
When it comes to exercise and stretching, the calf muscles typically don’t receive the amount of attention they deserve. However, our calves provide significant support to the lower body and are used in a wide range of activities, such as standing on your toes when you’re trying to reach something up high and walking. Because our calf muscles experience frequent use, they can easily become tense and create health problems, such as patellar tendonitis, plantar fasciitis, Achilles tendonitis, shin splints, knee pain, heel pain, and general foot pain. The aforementioned conditions are the very reason the Slant Board was developed. Multiple studies have indicated that using a Slant Board is a highly effective way to increase flexibility and relieve tightness in your calves. 
Our Slant Board, also referred to as an Incline Board or Calf Stretch Board, is made of strong, durable plywood with birch wood veneer. The incline of the board can be adjusted to 4 angle adjustments: 10, 20, 30, and 40 degrees. Our Slant Board features a firm, non-slip surface for foot placement as well as a non-skid surface on the bottom of the board. With an updated safe and simple locking system and pre-drilled holes to store locking screws our calf stretcher sets the standard for professional quality and design. With its extremely simple design and construction-quality hardware, our board will flip open and then fold closed for easy portability. This level of simplicity and quality means there is virtually no maintenance with your Rolling With It Slant Board.

title: Hack Squat Machine with Band Pegs, V Squat Machine with Adjustable Footboard, Plate Loaded Lower Body Special Leg Machine fit 2” Plate, 1000 LBS Capacity Calf Raise Machine for Home Gym,Red
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Weight Machines › Leg Machines
features: Comprehensive Security - V squat machine provides a fixed motion trajectory, which can help to accurately control the body's posture and avoid injuries caused by wrong posture during free squat. The safety bar makes it easy to select the right height, making exercise more convenient and comfortable, and the design of the lowest lockout position reduces the risk of injury. The non-slip texture of the footboard increases friction and prevents displacement during exercise.

Beyond the Traditional - Compared with traditional Hack Squat machines, the V Squat Machine provides greater stability and spreads the load more evenly throughout the lower limb muscle group to better balance the upper and middle leg joints. It is also more suitable for people with knee injuries while ensuring normal hip rotation within a natural range of motion.

Durable Construction - This product features a durable heavy-duty frame design with outstanding stability and reliability. The frame is made of 2mm thick high-strength steel, carefully designed and manufactured to ensure that it can withstand heavy loads and long-term use without deformation or damage. And the rubber base pads provide thoughtful protection for the floor. Max Weight Capacity:1000LBS.

Lower Extremity Strength Training - This innovative fitness equipment allows for easy targeting of the quadriceps, hamstrings, glutes, and calves through a variety of exercises. It’s the perfect choice for building leg strength, improving balance and stability, and sculpting a beautifully toned lower body.

aPlusContent.title: Product Description
aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
Tib Bar Tibialis Anterior Exercise Equipment 
Why Need Tib Bar? 
The tibialis anterior is the muscle that runs next to the shin bone, down the front of the leg from the knee to the ankle. When the tibialis anterior muscle is weak, undue force being generated through walking, running or jumping makes its way to the knee, causing knee pain and shin splints. 
Strengthening the tibialis anterior has been linked to a decrease in shin splints and knee pain. Using the Tib Bar also helps to strengthen the muscles, tendons and ligaments surrounding the ankle while simultaneously stretching and increasing the ankles range of motion. 
Product Features 
Length:12.99 inches 
Width:7.48 inches 
Height:5.11 inches 
Sleeve Diameter:2inches 
Accessories:1x Barbell Clamps 
Application:Leg Training 
Durable Steel Construction 
Use Durable Steel Construction,the weld is smooth without bulge,weight plates will be putting into smoothly.And spray is durable, use for a long time will not fall off. 
Fit 2’’ Plates 
The steel loading bar is compatible with 2’’ standard weight plates, which can be added to the weights you want for achieving the desired effect. 
High Quality Barbell Clamp 
Use High Quality Foam Pads on Tib Bar,make your leg training more comfortable. 
High Quality Barbell Clamp 
Use High Quality Barbell Clamp,tight and reliable.When you exercise, you don't have to worry about the plates swaying or slipping.

description: The Tib Bar is your ultimate solution for building leg, tibialis, and hamstring strength. Designed to fit both 1-inch and 2-inch weight plates, this versatile equipment ensures you can customize your workout to meet your fitness goals. Whether you're targeting the tibia, calf, or ankle muscles, this tool adapts seamlessly to your training routine. Ideal for both home and gym use, it's perfect for exercises like squat, tib raises, and calf extensions.Enhance your nordic and sit-up training with the included adjustable strap and foam pad. title: GMWD Vertical Leg Press Machine, Leg Strength Training Machine with Linear Bearing, Lower Body Special Machine Home Gym
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Weight Machines › Leg Machines
features: This vertical leg press machine is made of 50 x 100 mm, 14 gauge high quality steel. Gross weight: 94 lbs. Weight capacity: 550lbs. User height: higher than 5.3''.

Cost & Space Saving Choice: The GMWD vertical leg press machine is an excellent space saving machine. It's great for those who want to do leg press but don't have much space at home. Assemble size: 43.5’’ x 32.5’’ x 62’’. 50% less footprint than the normal 45°leg press machine. The full 1:1 ratio means that you don't need many weights, which is also a cost saving choice.

Ergonomic design: This leg machine has 3 positions backrest pad and head pad. Laying flat on the back pad, horizontally to the ground, your lower back, upper back, and neck, are almost completely left out of it. This can minimize lower back rounding and maintain your spine's natural curve. 5°Tilted and enlarged footboard is ergonomic and can be more comfortable while you are exercising.

Liner Bearing Design: Unlike other brands’ nylon bushings or roller bearings, we updated liner bearings. "Linear bearing" means a higher cost for GMWD but a better feeling for you. You won't feel any clogged while you're exercising. Start your leg training more coherently and smoothly.
3 start and end positions can meet the needs of people with different heights. Adjustable height range: 47.8'' to 62''. All your family members can enjoy the fun of leg strength training.
This leg press machine has 3 weight posts to help you add weights to your training. The detachable sleeves can fit both 1'' & 2'' plates.
Tilted and enlarged footboard is ergonomic and can be more comfortable while you are exercising. Leaflike texture for better slip resistance.

Why should I get this GMWD vertical leg press machine? 
“Compact"-is the answer from GMWD, which only requires a 43.5'' x 32.5'' area. If you want to build your leg muscle but the idea is stopped by the limited space. This leg machine is designed for you! 
Why choose vertical leg press machine not a 45° leg press machine? 
Vertical inverted stirrup machines avoid borrowed weight and you can feel the full 1:1 weight. 
You also don't need too many weights, which is also a cost-saving choice! 
What does the 'linear bearing" mean to me? 
"Linear bearing" means a higher cost for GMWD but a better feeling for you. You won't feel any clogged while you're exercising. Start your leg training more coherently and smoothly! 
What does this vertical leg press machine work for? 
Focus on your leg press training. Also, can do calf raises for a nice shaping calf. 
Is this vertical leg press machine suitable for beginners? 
Absolutely, an excellent choice for beginners to build their leg muscles.

title: Body-Solid (GSCR349B Seated Calf Raise Exercise Machine for Strength Training, Home Gym Equipment
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Home Gym Systems
description: Product DescriptionThe Body-Solid Seated Calf Raise Machine combines a user-friendly ergonomic design with advanced biomechanical engineering to give you an intense and focused workout on your calves. Designed to increase calf muscle interaction and help speed the rate of development, this calf fitness machine features a unique foot platform design that eliminates stress compression on the ball of your foot while providing maximum range of motion for deep muscle fiber penetration. With a 2- by 3-inch 11-gauge high-tensile strength steel mainframe, this calf workout machine is durably constructed to stand up to rigorous use in gyms and clubs. The weight carriage is designed with a 3: 1 weight ratio, which means any loaded weight will feel three times heavier. Precision pillow block and sealed ball bearings provide smooth, friction-free movement through every intense workout. Durable, 3-inch thick DuraFirm padding ensures you stay comfortable while you lift. When assembled, the Body-Solid Seated Calf Raise Machine measures 47 by 20 by 39 inches (L x W x H) and weighs 93 pounds. It is backed by the Body-Solid Lifetime In-Home and Full Commercial .Amazon.comThe Body-Solid GSCR349 Seated Calf Raise Machine offers a combination of user-friendly ergonomic design and advanced biomechanical engineering to optimize calf workouts. The machine is designed to increase calf muscle contraction and speed the rate of development, achieved via the unique foot platform design that eliminates stress compression on the ball of the foot, while providing optimal range of motion for deep muscle fiber penetration.  The weight carriage is designed for a three-to-one weight ratio, and pivots on a precision pillow block and sealed ball bearings for smooth, friction-free movement. To carry the heaviest loads, the mainframe is constructed of two-by-three-inch (W x D), 11-gauge high-tensile strength steel, making it ideal for high traffic, heavy use applications.  Durable, three-inch-thick DuraFirm padding is comfortable and supportive, and the unit measures 20-by-39-by-47 inches (W x H x D) when fully assembled. features: INDUSTRY LEADER: For 30+ years, Body Solid has held the widest array of products designed to meet the demands of the ever-changing fitness industry (home gym, free weight machines, treadmills, bikes, ellipticals, weight plates, kettlebells, dumbbells, flooring, accessories and more). Our products are cutting edge and reliable and are built for Life……Your Life.

DESIGNED FOR MAXIMUM PERFORMANCE: Our innovative foot platform design reduces strain on the balls of your feet, enabling a more extensive range of motion and improved muscle building. Coupled with a 3:1 weight ratio carriage and top-of-the-line pillow block and sealed ball bearings, this machine ensures an intense and effective workout, promoting explosive growth in calf muscles.

ENHANCED COMFORT AND EASE: With plush DuraFirm knee and seat pads, the Body-Solid machine offers a cozy experience, ideal for extended workout sessions. Its compact design makes it a perfect fit for home gyms, saving valuable space. Additionally, its weight plates, collars, and adapter sleeves are available separately, providing complete customization to match your fitness level and aspirations.

INTUITIVE DESIGN FOR EVERY ATHLETE: Equipped with adjustable knee and seat pads, this machine caters to users of all sizes, guaranteeing a comfortable fit for everyone. Its angled, non-slip foot platform boosts safety and stability during exercises, while the standard 1" plate post simplifies weight adjustments (Olympic adapter sleeve sold separately), ensuring a seamless workout experience.

BUILT TO LAST: Constructed with a heavy-duty 2" x 3" 11-gauge high-tensile strength steel main frame, this can withstand the most rigorous and frequent calf-blasting workouts, making it an ideal choice for high-traffic gyms and clubs. Measures 47"x23"x39" and weighs 93lbs. Lifetime manufacutrer warranty on frame & welds.

title: Calf Raise Machine Home Gym: Calf Machine Seated Calf Raise Machine Adjustable Calf Workout Machine Exercise Equipment
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Weight Machines › Leg Machines
description: Custom-tailored for fitness enthusiasts, calf raise machine features adjustable height and horizontal distance settings to accommodate users of various heights. Its robust steel frame not only ensures safety but also delivers professional-grade calf training. The ergonomic seat design helps maintain proper exercise posture, effectively enhancing strength and sculpting calf contours. It supports both dumbbell training and resistance band workouts for increased intensity. Additionally, it is compatible with 1-inch and 2-inch weight plates, offering a comprehensive calf shaping solution for trainers at all levels. sales do not include weight plate
features: WORK OUT YOUR CALVES AT HOME: Calf raise machine customized for home gym. The improved design of the barbell rack increases the range of motion, upgrading your daily training. Focused on calf muscle training and stretching, it allows you to effortlessly enhance strength and sculpt calf contours in the comfort of your own environment.

POWERFUL SUPPORT STRUCTURE:Calf machine built with 12 gauge steel and a stable triangular frame, ensures safety and stability in every workout. Its robust design offers a dependable base for your routines, empowering you to confidently reach your fitness goals. The entire unit supports a weight capacity of 550LBS.

4+5 ADJUSTABLE SETTINGS: Leg raise machine with 4 height and 5 positions adjustable for fore and aft distance., it accommodates a variety of training needs. The thigh supports and cushioned seat offer a comfortable, ergonomic workout, ensuring everyone can find their ideal training position. Fits users up to 6 feet tall.

DIVERSE TRAINING OPTIONS: Seated Calf Raise Machine is designed for workouts with barbell plates and can also have resistance bands attached to its side hooks to increase the intensity of the training and effectively sculpt the leg muscles. It can also be used with elastic bands alone for calf stretching. ( YOUR PACKAGE INCLUDES ELASTIC BANDS AND BARBELL CLAMPS)
DETACHABLE 1-INCH AND 2-INCH SLEEVES：Removable sleeve weight holder of this calf workout machine is compatible with 1" and 2" weight plates. (Weight plates are not included)

INSTALLATION & AFTER-SALES: Comes with an instruction manual for easy assembly. If you have any questions, please feel free to contact us at any time. We will strive to resolve your issues promptly and ensure your complete satisfaction.

aPlusContent.title: Product Description
aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
The video showcases the product in use.The video guides you through product setup.The video compares multiple products.The video shows the product being unpacked.
How do you use the CalfPRO? 
Place the CalfPRO against the wall or in the door jam. With shoes on, or off, place your heel into the heel lock and gently lean forward towards the door frame. As your calf stretches, pull yourself closer to the frame to deepen the stretch. 
Is the angle adjustable? 
No, The device is designed to be one angle so that your calf length can be the variable. The closer you come to the wall, the deeper the stretch. The angle was designed to work for all people tall & short, young & old & should not be adjusted 
How does the CalfPRO differ from traditional calf stretching methods? 
Unlike manual stretching or basic equipment, the CalfPRO offers users unparalleled control over the stretching process by allowing them to lock in the back of the heel, ensuring a targeted stretch of the calf muscles every time. 
Can the CalfPRO be used by individuals of all fitness levels, including beginners? 
Yes! Beginners can increase the intensity of the stretch as their flexibility improves over time. The CalfPRO's ergonomic design helps minimize strain on the body, making it great for users who may be new to stretching or have limited flexibility. 
Can the CalfPRO be easily stored when not in use? 
Whether you're using it at home, in the gym, or on the go, the CalfPRO can be quickly and easily stowed away thanks to its collapsible design, making it a convenient addition to any fitness routine.

items.text:
Ultra-Soft Heel Pad 
Built with durable but soft slip-resistant TPR foam, the CalfPRO gives you maximum comfort and security while you stretch.

Feel the stretch throughout your entire body
In just one use, you'll notice an extreme sense of comfort & relief throughout your feet, calves & hamstrings. The tension will dissipate after each use.

Collapsible and Compact
CalfPRO is fully collapsible, compact and portable. Simply fold it, stuff it in your bag and you’re good to go! No more tight calves on your travels — get clinical grade stretching anywhere, anytime.

Leveraged Heel Lock
The CalfPRO comfortably sets your heel as an immovable fulcrum and softly cradles your ankle at a perfect pivot point so you can get the deepest stretch.

Strong as Steel
Okay, it’s NOT made of steel, but it might as well be! CalfPRO uses a strong ABS Plastic that has the tensile strength of steel without the weight. Strong enough to carry 300+ lbs of weight

Patented Door Jam Groove
The door frame is an excellent place to provide both the stabilization and leverage you need for a safe, effective calf stretch.

items.text: Yes! Beginners can increase the intensity of the stretch as their flexibility improves over time. The CalfPRO's ergonomic design helps minimize strain on the body, making it great for users who may be new to stretching or have limited flexibility.

items.name: Can the CalfPRO be easily stored when not in use?
items.text: Whether you're using it at home, in the gym, or on the go, the CalfPRO can be quickly and easily stowed away thanks to its collapsible design, making it a convenient addition to any fitness routine.

aiReviewsSummary.text: Customers find that the footrest provides a good calf stretch and helps relieve pain. They appreciate its sturdy build quality, effectiveness, and long-lasting durability. Many find it easy to use, comfortable, and effective for stretching their legs and feet. However, opinions differ on whether it offers good value for money.

features: [STABILTY & POSTURE SUPPORT] This slant board for squats is designed to help support the mobility and flexibility of your ankles, knees, and buttocks by raising your heels. Our elevated heel wedge for squat helps you maintain a balanced posture to reduce strain on your back, knees, and hips to elevate your workouts.

The slant board for squats uses a 2-piece construction and offers 3 adjustable levels up to 25° (10° +15°). It includes storage bag makes it a breeze to carry and store.

[HIGH DENSITY & DURABLE] Our squat wedges for weightlifting are made using high density rubber for long term use with a non-slip texture to make sure our calf raise blocks are durable enough to support up to 1300 lbs. while helping you maintain balance during workouts even in the long run.

[VERSATILE EXERCISE SUPPORT] Our heavy-duty squat wedges blocks feature a wide, flat bottom and long ramp length to offer a wide range of uses to support both upper and lower body exercises. These elevated squat wedge blocks are suitable for Pilates, stretching, squats, push-ups, deadlifts, weightlifting, etc.

[USEFUL ACCESSORIES] The resistance band helps maintain proper alignment and posture, ensuring correct squat technique. aPlusContent.title: Product Description
aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
Get More Out of Every Rep 
Once you start squatting with these wedge blocks, you won’t go back to doing it flat-footed. They'll help you increase your squat depth and range of motion, taking 'leg day' to a whole new level. 
Max Out Quad Engagement 
Raising your heels with these wedges will help you fully engage your muscles, particularly the quads and glutes, so you'll feel the burn in all the right places, maximizing strength and growth. 
Makes It Easy to Squat Safely 
Many lifters struggle with maintaining proper squat form, but these innovative ramps make it easy to keep a balanced posture throughout the movement, taking the strain off your back, knees, and hips. 
Not Just for Smarter Squatting 
Another big benefit of these wedge blocks is their versatility. They allow you to engage different muscle groups, making Pilates, stretching, push-ups, deadlifts, and lunges even more challenging and effective. 
Tough, but Not a Drag to Carry 
They're made from high-density rubber and can support up to 2,000 lbs without breaking a sweat. But despite their impressive strength, the hollowed design makes them surprisingly lightweight and portable. 
Non-Slip & Simple to Adjust 
Our squat wedge blocks have a non-slip surface, so you stay firmly planted throughout your entire lift. They're also adjustable, allowing you to quickly modify the angle to three different heights: 25° (10° + 15°). 
Designed for Every Foot Size 
Each weightlifting wedge measures 8.5" L x 5.7" W x 3.77" H, making them the perfect fit for feet small and large. They're compact enough to store easily, but large enough to provide a stable, secure base. 
Blocks + Bands = Epic Gains 
Our adjustable squat wedges also come with two premium resistance bands. They'll help you increase resistance during squats, target different muscle groups, and incorporate full-body exercises.

aPlusContent.title: Product Description
aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
Enhance Your Squat Performance with HarderWill Squat Wedge! 
Take your squat training to the next level with our Squat Wedge — the ultimate tool designed to improve your mobility, form, and performance. Whether you're a beginner or an experienced lifter, the Squat Wedge is an essential addition to your workout routine. 
If you struggle with limited ankle dorsiflexion, our Squat Wedge helps increase your range of motion, allowing your knees to travel further forward while keeping your heels grounded. This enables deeper, more effective squats without compromising your form. 
The Squat Wedge assists in maintaining proper squat technique by encouraging proper knee tracking and reducing the tendency to lean forward too much. This means less strain on your lower back and more focus on building strength in your legs and glutes. 
For those with tight calves or ankle mobility issues, the Squat Wedge can alleviate discomfort during squats by promoting a more natural movement pattern. It’s perfect for preventing knee pain, lower back strain, or ankle discomfort often experienced during deep squats. 
By lifting your heels slightly, the Squat Wedge allows you to squat deeper with better balance and control. This improved depth results in better muscle activation, particularly targeting the quads, hamstrings, and glutes. 
Made from high-quality, durable materials, our Squat Wedge is designed to last. Its compact, portable size makes it easy to use at home or in the gym. Whether you're training for strength, mobility, or overall fitness, it’s the perfect addition to your workout gear.

features: Durable Construction: Expertly crafted using heavy-duty steel construction and thick foam cushions to ensure long-lasting, comfortable use, the LoGest Adjustable Tibialis Bar knees over toes equipment is designed to provide you with great workout sessions for years to come.

Minimizes Injury: LoGest’s Adjustable Tib Bar strength training leg machines stretches and strengthens the tibialis anterior while reinforcing your muscles, ligaments and tendons surrounding the ankles, tibia dorsi calf machine helping to reduce injury and prevent chronic leg pain, knee pain and shin splints.

aPlusContent.title: Product Description
aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
Build up Strength and Power with LoGest. 
Exercise your tibialis, knees, shins and ankles to build up strength and prevent injuries. A perfect way to effectively target different groups of muscles, the LoGest Adjustable Tib Bar calf workout machine is easy to set up and securely lock weight plates in place with the included barbell collar. This equipment is durably crafted using high-quality material to ensure long-term durability calves machine, featuring plush foam cushions for optimal comfort while you’re performing full ankle rotation curls, tib raises, leg raises and other exercises. 
Heavy-Duty Construction. 
The LoGest Adjustable Tib Bar calves exercise equipment is a great choice for anyone who wishes to strengthen their tibialis, knees, shins and ankles; prevent injuries and improve athletic performance. Boasting an exceptionally strong build, this exercise calf workout equipment is expertly constructed using a combination of thick, plush foam cushions for optimal comfort during leg training and solid steel construction for durability. The steel material is furnished with a black-coated finish to prevent rust and corrosion, ensuring long-term strength and reliable use for years to come. 
Strengthens the Tibialis. 
Measuring 14.20" L x 16.7" H in size when not extended, the LoGest calf exercise machine boasts a compact design that will take up limited space in your home. Plus, it conveniently folds to the side so it’s parallel to the wall, taking up even less space wherever it’s mounted. Built to last throughout all of your workouts, this simple piece of equipment allows you to turn any room in your home into a personal gym. 
Improve Tibialis Strength with LoGest’s Adjustable Tib Bar. 
Easy to Adjust. 
Stop struggling with Tib Bars that don’t accommodate your large foot size. For added convenience and to meet your individual needs, the LoGest Tib Bar calf raise equipment is height adjustable. Simply turn the knob and pull the orange bar up or down to change the position and it locks back in place. This allows you to adjust the height from 8 inches up to 12 inches to best meet your personal foot size. 
Compact Design. 
Measuring 12.5" W x 16.75" L in size, the LoGest Adjustable Tib Bar calf machine home gym boasts a compact design that will take up limited space in your home. Plus, it features an adjustable height to accommodate different foot sizes – measuring 8 inches when closed and 12 inches when fully extended. Built to last throughout all of your workouts, this simple piece of equipment allows you to turn any room in your home into a personal gym or can be easily packed in your gym bag for on-the-go training tib bar exercise. 
Keeps Plates Secure. 
Place your 2-inch Olympic plates onto the bar, ensuring they’re pushed up against the barbell clamp and secured tightly with the locking clamp. Once secure, you can begin engaging in your exercises tibialis anterior exercise equipment – including full ankle rotation curls, tib raises, leg raises, squats, bench pullovers and more – without having to worry about the plates swaying or slipping off of the equipment.

title: XMARK Seated Leg Extension and Leg Curl Machine, Lower Body Adjustable Leg Exercise Machine, Weight Plate Loaded Leg Rotary Extension
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Weight Machines › Leg Machines
features: Strong hamstrings and quadriceps are crucial for balance, speed, and coordination. XMARK’s rotary leg extension and curl machine isolates the quadriceps and hamstrings while providing a full range of motion through each movement.

XMARK’s top of the line leg extension and curl machine, the XM-7615 is designed with 12-position vertically-adjustable thigh pads, a 20-position adjustable press arm to fit various leg lengths, and a fully adjustable backrest pad to meet your needs.

Use the weight plates you already own for an excellent lower body workout. Both standard and Olympic weight plates are supported with the XMARK Rotary Leg Machine. Included is a 14" chrome Olympic adapter sleeve for use with Olympic weight plates.

Assembly of this specialized leg machine is straightforward and hassle free. The included easy-to-follow instructions are very clear and will have you setup and ready to exercise in no time with minimal effort.

This is a high quality leg curl machine weighing 125 lbs and features a 11-gauge steel 2x3" mainframe, extra thick cushions, and a rear weight plate post for exceptional stability, support, and comfort during intense workouts under heavy load. You'll never want to miss leg day again!

Product Description
XMark Leg Curl Machine with Rotary Leg Extension 
Want to take your leg workouts to the next level? XMARK's Leg Extension and Curl Machine features a rock-solid steel frame and fully adjustable components for a punishing workout on your quads and hamstrings. Transition smoothly between exercises and push your limits. 
Features 
EXTRA THICK CUSHIONS 
Features extra-thick 3-inch Duraguard vinyl cushions and pads that are resistant to sweat and tears, and enhance comfort and stability during use. 
13" LOADABLE SLEEVE 
A 225 lb loadable weight capacity allows you to gradually increase the weight lifted to stimulate muscle growth, known as progressive overload. 
HIGHLY ADJUSTABLE 
20-position press arm, 12-position vertically-adjustable thigh pads, and a fully adjustable backrest ensure proper form and muscle isolation. 
PLATE STORAGE 
While not in use, store your bumper or Olympic plates at the back of your machine on this 13" plate storage.

aPlusContent.title: Product Description
aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
DESIGNED WITH EMPATHY 
ENHANCED PERFORMANCE 
Our squat wedges instantly improve squat form by reducing the effect of poor mobility and unlocking flexibility at the ankle, knee, and hip. 
Elevating the heels at an optimal height during squats allows greater muscle recruitment, and can help relieve lower back stress and minimize the risk of injury by keeping your posture more upright under load. 
DEEPER SQUATS 
With this professional squat wedge, you can choose from different levels of elevation up to 2.35-inch and 10-degree, 
which is high enough to encourage an upright position and help you get deeper squats in an efficient way. 
EXCELLENT STABILITY 
The squat platform features a textured surface that prevents your feet from slipping during exercise, 
and rubber bumpers whose role is to keep the wedge in place on any type of surface, so you can stay focused on your training. 
ORDER WITH CONFIDENCE 
Your satisfaction is our top priority, so we strive to provide you with the best products and service. 
If for any reason you are not completely satisfied with our squat wedge, we will give you a full refund upon return or a free replacement with no questions asked. 
VERSATILE FITNESS USE 
Not only can help improve your squats and calf raises but this squat wedge for weight lifting can also be used for a wide range of exercises and fitness purposes, such as yoga stretches, planks, push-ups, or as a calf block. 
PRACTICAL DESIGN 
These squat blocks are 7-inch wide and 13-inch long, offering enough space to place your feet more comfortably. 
Also, the wedge is designed with slots for resistance bands, so you can use them during training without worrying about slipping or rolling forward. 

Our Vision 
We believe that successful training is not possible without the right gear and accessories. 
That is why Double Circle has dedicated entirely to create simple and reliable accessories whose only purpose is to help you train more effectively and without any injuries. 
DOUBLE CIRCLE SQUAT WEDGE 
10 Degree Elevation 
This professional gym-grade squat wedge block was designed with your safety and comfort in mind, as it has a durable construction with excellent elevation levels that can instantly improve mobility and flexibility for your ankles, knees, and hips.

Non-slip design equipped with rubber bumpers and a textured surface

title: Nexo Calf Raise Block - Commercial-Grade Steel Heavy Duty 1,000lbs Capacity for Calf Workouts
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Weight Machines › Leg Machines
features: Improved Athletic Performance: Strong calves are essential for activities that require running, jumping, and explosive movements, such as sprinting, basketball, soccer, and dancing. Powerful calf muscles provide the necessary propulsion and stability to excel in these activities.

Prevention of Injury: Strong calves help to stabilize the ankles and lower legs, reducing the risk of injuries such as ankle sprains, Achilles tendonitis, and shin splints. They also absorb shock during high-impact activities, protecting the joints and bones from excessive stress.

Enhanced Balance and Stability: Well-developed calf muscles contribute to overall balance and stability, particularly during activities that require changes in direction or quick movements. They help maintain proper alignment of the lower body, reducing the risk of falls and improving coordination.

Functional Movement: Strong calves are essential for everyday movements such as walking, climbing stairs, and standing for long periods. They provide the necessary strength and endurance to perform these tasks efficiently and without fatigue.

Aesthetic Appeal: Well-defined calf muscles can enhance the appearance of the legs, creating a more sculpted and toned look. This can boost confidence and self-esteem, especially for individuals who engage in activities where leg aesthetics are important, such as bodybuilding or fitness competitions.

UNMERA Foam Incline slant board 
What is the main cause of plantar fasciitis? 
Due to the long-term effects of overload pressure, acute or chronic damage to the plantar fascia is the main cause of pain. 
The most common reason is that they often walk for a long time, including mountain climbing, hiking, shopping and other activities.
Walking for a few days in a row can easily cause chronic damage to the soles of the feet, leading to plantar fasciitis. 
In addition, there are structural factors that cause abnormal tension of the plantar fascia, such as flat feet, high arch feet, and short heel tendons. In the long term, the waist, hips, knees, ankles, etc. may be caused by improper posture during walking Pain.

modules.text:
What is the main cause of plantar fasciitis? 
Due to the long-term effects of overload pressure, acute or chronic damage to the plantar fascia is the main cause of pain. 
The most common reason is that they often walk for a long time, including mountain climbing, hiking, shopping and other activities.
Walking for a few days in a row can easily cause chronic damage to the soles of the feet, leading to plantar fasciitis. 
In addition, there are structural factors that cause abnormal tension of the plantar fascia, such as flat feet, high arch feet, and short heel tendons. In the long term, the waist, hips, knees, ankles, etc. may be caused by improper posture during walking Pain.

aPlusContent.title: Product Description
aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
The video showcases the product in use.The video guides you through product setup.The video compares multiple products.The video shows the product being unpacked.
Why Need Tib Bar？ 
The benefits of adding tibialis anterior extension and exercise to training: 

Everyone should stretch and strengthen the tibialis anterior muscle. This small muscle is very important for our sports, especially for those who participate in running or jumping activities. The strong and relaxed tibialis anterior muscle can help counteract the negative impact of the high impact force of the feet constantly hitting the ground. 
Reduce the risk of calf, ankle and foot injuries 
Reduce the chance of anterior tibial tendinitis 
Low risk of shin splinting pain & stress fractures 
The video showcases the product in use.The video guides you through product setup.The video compares multiple products.The video shows the product being unpacked.
Fitarc Tib Bar Assembly 
Here is the instruction of assembling Fitarc Tib Bar 

Please don't worry about assembly problems, we are equipped with installation videos and instructions, you can check them at any time. 
4 Foam Pads 
Different from others, in order to make exercise more comfortable, we have added 2 foam pads on the original basis to give you a better experience. 
High-Quality Snap 
FITARC use high quality snap, tight and reliable. Effectively fix the barbell plate to prevent back and forth shaking. 
Limit Pin 
The special design prevents the buckle from slipping due to the excessive weight of the weight plate, double protection and fixation. 
2 inch / 1 inch diameter 
Use 9" Extension Loading Bar, 2 sizes to choose from. Suitable for 2 inch Plates or 1 inch dumbbell pieces (depending on the size you purchase). 
How to Use Tib Bar? 
Place the weight plate with a 2-inch hole diameter on the bar, and fasten it with the snap and limit pins. Sitting on a flat surface, you need to support your thighs and knees and straighten your calves. Then tib bar hooks easily over the end of the foot for full rotation of the ankle up and down. 
Kettlebell Replacement 
Sit-ups (fixed) 
Is the collar easy to use? Is it too tight? 
A little tight but holds the weight plates firmly. 
I lost a screw, what should I do? 
I lost one recently during disassembling, contacted the seller and they sent me a screw set right away. 
Are the bars welded vertically? Will it be crooked? I've seen this problem reflected in the reviews of other brands. 
Mine is normal, and I don’t feel the weight tilting in any direction when using it. 
Has it been effective? 
I've been using it for a few days and feel a noticeable improvement on my shin muscles, so I'm ready to work on my knees and ankles next. 
Do I need to install the foam myself? 
No, the seller has already installed it. I have purchased WIN*** before. It is not convenient to remove and replace, and the foam is not as big as that of Fitarc.
