title: Squat Wedge Elevated Squats Block: Portable Knees Over Toes Ergonomic Equipment Calf Raise Exercise Platform for Full Range of Motion Improve Strength Stability and Mobility
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Weight Machines › Leg Machines
description: Improved squat mechanics: The inclined platform of the Wedge helps to enhance your squat mechanics by elevating your heels. This promotes a more upright posture and better knee alignment, allowing you to achieve a deeper position with improved form. By optimizing your mechanics, you can target the muscles more effectively and reduce the risk of strain or injury. Enhanced muscle engagement: Elevating your heels with the board shifts the weight distribution, placing greater emphasis on your quadriceps muscles. This increased muscle engagement helps to strengthen and develop your quadriceps, resulting in improved lower body strength and power. Reduced strain on lower back and knees: The proper alignment facilitated by the platform reduces strain on your lower back and knees. By promoting a more upright posture and distributing the load evenly, it minimizes the risk of excessive stress on these areas, making it a valuable tool for individuals with lower back or knee sensitivities. Suitable for all fitness levels: Whether you are a professional athlete or a beginner, it is designed to accommodate all fitness levels. It provides essential support for beginners who are still developing proper exercise mechanics and mobility, while also challenging experienced athletes to achieve greater depth and muscle activation in their exercise. Versatility for various exercises: While primarily used for heel elevated, it is also a versatile tool for other exercises. It can be utilized for calf raises, split squats, deadlifts, and more. Its ergonomic design promotes comfortable and effective stretches, making it suitable for yoga enthusiasts and those focusing on rehabilitation or flexibility training. Portable and durable: It is made from high-quality, durable materials, ensuring long-lasting performance. Its lightweight and compact design make it easy to transport, allowing you to enjoy the benefits of an elevated squat wherever you go – whether at home, in the gym or traveling.
features: Optimized Squat Mechanics and Muscle Engagement: The workout wedges plays a crucial role in optimizing squat mechanics by improving ankle mobility and body alignment. By elevating the heels, it enables a deeper position, reducing strain on the lower back and minimizing knee discomfort. This improved alignment not only helps maintain proper spinal posture but also ensures optimal muscle engagement in key areas such as the quadriceps, glutes, and core, resulting in enhanced strength gains

Support for Pro/Beginners and Joint Protection: With its ability to enhance squat form, the incline wedge serves as a valuable tool for both pro and beginners. It provides essential support for those who are still developing proper exercise mechanics and mobility. By elevating the heels, it assists in achieving a more upright posture, reducing the risk of leaning forward excessively, and promoting better joint alignment

Yoga and Rehabilitation Aid: This versatile slant board is designed for yoga enthusiasts and rehabilitation purposes. It offers effective stretch and stability, assisting in holding intense stretches without straining sensitive joints. Its portable and durable construction allows for convenient use at home, in the gym, or on the go. Use it for plantar fasciitis rehab, hamstring mobility exercises, or deep, centered stretches to enhance flexibility and physical well-being

Functional Strength Training Support: With its incline design, this slant board is a valuable tool for strength training exercises like deadlifts, ATG, goblet squats, and split squats. It promotes comfortable, deep stretches of the hamstrings and shins, optimizing muscle engagement. Its sturdy construction ensures secure support, making it suitable for use in garage gyms or yoga studios. Incorporate this versatile gear to improve both strength and flexibility during your workouts

Stretching Essential: This Portable slant wedge is an essential accessory for daily stretching routine. It offers effective stretch and stability, assisting in holding intense stretches without straining sensitive joints. Its durable construction ensures long-lasting support, while its ergonomic design promotes deeper, more centered stretches. Whether you're a beginner or an experienced practitioner, this versatile slant board is a valuable addition to enhance your yoga and stretching sessions
